<location>
    <name>Magic Quaters</name>
    <npcs>
        <npc>Magician</npc>
    </npcs>
    <pres>
        <present>Mage</present>
    </pres>
    <quests>
        <repeatableQuest>
            <name>Q2.1</name>
            <description>Talk to the magician</description>
            <dialogue>
                Well met. Welcome to the magic quaters. This is where we do.. well.. magic!z
            </dialogue>
            <choices>
                <choice>C2.1.1</choice>
                <choice>C2.1.2</choice>
                <choice>C2.1.3</choice>
                <choice>C2.1.4</choice>
            </choices>
        </repeatableQuest>
        <oneshotQuest>
            <name>Q2.2</name>
            <description>Something brewing at the brothel</description>
            <pres>
                <effect>Magician Happy</effect>
                <global>
                    <has>!Reveal Wench</has>
                </global>
            </pres>
            <dialogue>
                Hello, yes. Good to see you again my friend. There is something most urgent I need to discuss with you.
            </dialogue>
            <choices>
                <choice>C2.2.1</choice>
                <choice>C2.2.2</choice>
                <choice>C2.2.3</choice>
            </choices>
        </oneshotQuest>
        <oneshotQuest>
            <name>Q2.3</name>
            <description>
                A hidden shadow
            </description>
            <pres>
                <global>
                    <has>Reveal Wench</has>
                </global>
            </pres>
            <dialogue>
                I do not believe it! A succubus! In the middle of the town - how could I not see this!
            </dialogue>
            <choices>
                <choice>C2.3.1</choice>
                <choice>C2.3.2</choice>
            </choices>
        </oneshotQuest>
        <oneshotQuest>
            <name>Q2.4</name>
            <description>The truth shall be ours!</description>
            <pres>
                <effect>Amulet</effect>
                <Coop/>
            </pres>
            <dialogue>
                You found the amulet! Amazing! Let me see it!
            </dialogue>
            <choices>
                <choice>C2.4.1</choice>
                <choice>C2.4.2</choice>
            </choices>
        </oneshotQuest>
        <randomQuest>
            <name>R2a</name>
            <extranpc>
                <npc>Wench</npc>
            </extranpc>
            <pres>
                <effect>Wench Happy</effect>
                <effect>!Wench Companion</effect>
                <global>
                    <has>Reveal Wench</has>
                </global>
            </pres>
            <dialogue>
                My powers are beyond that of this realm! 
                You should take me with you on your quest for the amulet.
            </dialogue>
            <choices>
                <choice>C2a.1</choice>
                <choice>C2a.2</choice>
            </choices>
        </randomQuest>
    </quests>
    <choices>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.1.1</name>
            <description>Archmage Azorag, it’s an honor.</description>
            <pres>
                <class>Mage</class>
            </pres>
            <results>
                <description priority="1">
                    Hello Brilliac, allways a pleasure to see one of the academies finest.
                </description>
                <effectResults>
                    <effect>Magician Happy</effect>
                </effectResults>
                <dialogueResult>
                    <dialogue>D2.1.1.1</dialogue>
                </dialogueResult>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.1.2</name>
            <results>
                <description priority="3">
                    Yes the Amulet has a great power and great wisdom.
                </description>
                <choicesResults>
                    <choice>C2.1.2.1</choice>
                </choicesResults>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.1.3</name>
            <pres>
                <class>Thief</class>
            </pres>
            <results>
                <description priority="2">
                    I'm surprised they didn’t stop you at the door Marcus. From what I’ve heard you are a bit too up close and personal.
                </description>
                <effectResults>
                    <effect>Magician Angry</effect>
                </effectResults>
                <dialogueResult>
                    <dialogue>D2.1.3.1</dialogue>
                </dialogueResult>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.1.4</name>
            <description>
                Sorry to disturb you Archmage. I’ll will be leaving now.
            </description>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.1.2.1</name>
            <description>
                Do you have any idea about where we could find this amulet?
            </description>
            <results>
                <description priority="3">
                    Sadly, no. It was lost to the world a thousands years ago, as you might know.
                    There has however been strange reports from the temple outside of the village. 
                    If i were you i would go there. But be careful it’s a dangerous place.
                </description>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.2.1</name>
            <description>Yes? Tell me more?</description>
            <results>
                <description>
                    There are dark things looking for the amulet. 
                    You must go to the brothel and try to discover what is hidden there. 
                    I sense something very dark and disturbing. 
                    You will need to use magical powers there.
                </description>
                <choicesResults>
                    <choice>C2.2.1.1</choice>
                    <choice>C2.2.1.2</choice>
                    <choice>C2.2.1.3</choice>
                </choicesResults>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.2.2</name>
            <description>First, tell me more about the Amulet</description>
            <results>
                <description>
                    The Amulet was created by the old gods.. 
                    It is called the Amulet of Samarkand, and is told to protect the wearer from evil spirits.
                </description>
                <dialogueResult>
                    <dialogue>D2.2.2.1</dialogue>
                </dialogueResult>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.2.3</name>
            <description>
                Sorry to disturb you Archmage. I’ll will be leaving now.
            </description>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.2.1.1</name>
            <description>
                Brothels are of little concern for me… Do you have anything more interesting?
            </description>
            <pres>
                <KnowsLocation>!Temple</KnowsLocation>
            </pres>
            <results>
                <description>
                    If i tell you about something then it is important.. Nevermind.. 
                    If you do not care then perhaps you are not worthy of the task. 
                    You can look to the temple outside the village - maybe that will satistfy your need for adventure.
                </description>
                <locationResults>
                    <location>Temple</location>
                </locationResults>
                <effectResults>
                    <effect>Magician Angry</effect>
                </effectResults>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.2.1.2</name>
            <pres>
                
            </pres>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.2.1.3</name>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.3.1</name>
            <description>What do we do about it?</description>
            <pres>
                <effect>!Key</effect>
            </pres>
            <results>
                <effectResults>
                    <effect>Key</effect>
                </effectResults>
                <locationResults>
                    <location>Temple</location>
                </locationResults>
                <description>
                    Hurry to the temple, take this key it should help you get inside!
                    Do not go back to the brothel - it is too dangerous!
                </description>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.3.2</name>
            <description>What do we do about it?</description>
            <pres>
                <effect>Key</effect>
            </pres>
            <results>
                <description>You must use the key at the temple quick!</description>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.4.1</name>
            <description>The amulet is mine! You must die!</description>
            <results>
                <effectResults>
                    <global>
                        <has>Magician Elminated</has>
                    </global>
                </effectResults>
                <wingame/>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2.4.2</name>
            <description>Here you go, let's uncover this together.</description>
            <results>
                <effectResults>
                    <effect>Magician Companion</effect>
                    <effect>!Amulet</effect>
                </effectResults>
                <wingame/>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2a.1</name>
            <description>Die filth!</description>
            <results>
                <effectResults>
                    <global>
                        <has>Wench Elminated</has>
                    </global>
                </effectResults>
            </results>
        </choice>
        <choice>
            <name>C2a.2</name>
            <description>You could prove usefull, want to join our party?</description>
            <results>
                <effectResults>
                    <effect>Wench Companion</effect>
                </effectResults>
            </results>
        </choice>
    </choices>
    <dialogues>
        <dialogue>
            <name>D2.1.1.1</name>
            <pres>
                <present>Mage</present>
                <present>Thief</present>
                <results>
                    <dialogue class="Mage">
                        The pleasure is all mine. Are you still working with pyrotechnics?
                    </dialogue>
                    <dialogue class="NPC">
                        Yes it is very exciting stuff. Altough quite dangerous aswell, perhaps even more so than magic.
                    </dialogue>
                    <dialogue class="Thief">
                        Pyrotechnics I'm not sure i like the sound of that...
                    </dialogue>
                </results>
            </pres>
        </dialogue>
        <dialogue>
            <name>D2.1.3.1</name>
            <pres>
                <present>Mage</present>
            </pres>
            <results>
                <dialogue class="Mage">
                    Magic is not something to fear Marcus. Not in the right hands.
                </dialogue>
                <dialogue class="Thief">
                    I do not fear it. Just too many fools playing with fire...
                </dialogue>
            </results>
        </dialogue>
        <dialogue>
            <name>D2.2.2.1</name>
            <pres>
                <present>Mage</present>
            </pres>
            <results>
                <dialogue class="Mage">
                    I hear that this amulet contains a very powerful magical entity that is absorbing the power. 
                    This is why you are protected.
                </dialogue>
                <dialogue class="Thief">
                    This amulet sounds very dangerous, what if this magical entity was let loose on the world?
                </dialogue>
                <dialogue class="Mage">
                    Well it would probably wreak havoc on the world. But don't worry about it. 
                    It is safely contained inside the amulets crystal.
                </dialogue>
            </results>
        </dialogue>
    </dialogues>
</location>
